# 🛒 Retail Sales Analysis Project

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes a retail sales dataset to extract meaningful business insights.  
The objective is to perform data cleaning, preprocessing, exploratory data analysis, and dashboard creation using Python and Power BI.

This project was completed as part of the ApexPlanet Internship Program.

